### ============================================================================
### 1. MODUL STATIC PAYMENT METHODS (REFACTOR)
### ============================================================================

### Get All Static Payment Methods
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenant/static-payment-methods?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create Static Payment Method (Bank)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenant/static-payment-methods
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "channel_type": "bank_account",
    "label": "Rekening Infaq Masjid",
    "bank_name": "BSI",
    "bank_branch": "Yogyakarta Sudirman",
    "account_number": "1234567890",
    "account_holder_name": "Takmir Masjid Al-Ikhlas",
    "sort_order": 1,
    "is_public": true
}

###

### Update Static Payment Method
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tenant/static-payment-methods/{{staticPaymentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "channel_type": "bank_account",
    "label": "Rekening Infaq Masjid (Updated)",
    "bank_name": "BSI",
    "account_number": "1234567890",
    "account_holder_name": "Takmir Masjid Al-Ikhlas",
    "sort_order": 1,
    "is_public": true
}

###

### Delete Static Payment Method
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tenant/static-payment-methods/{{staticPaymentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================================================
### 2. MODUL FINANCE - PG CONFIG (PAYMENT GATEWAY)
### ============================================================================

### Get PG Config
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenant/pg-config
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Upsert PG Config (Gunakan PG Pusat)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tenant/pg-config
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "use_central_pg": true,
    "provider": "etakmir_pusat",
    "client_key": "",
    "server_key": "",
    "is_production": false
}

###

### Upsert PG Config (Gunakan PG Midtrans Mandiri Masjid)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tenant/pg-config
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "use_central_pg": false,
    "provider": "midtrans",
    "client_key": "SB-Mid-client-contoh123",
    "server_key": "SB-Mid-server-contoh123",
    "is_production": false
}

### ============================================================================
### 3. MODUL FINANCE - CAMPAIGNS (ADMIN TENANT)
### ============================================================================

### Get All Campaigns (Pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenant/campaigns?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create Campaign
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenant/campaigns
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Pembebasan Lahan Parkir Masjid",
    "description": "Donasi untuk pembebasan lahan parkir seluas 200m2 di samping masjid.",
    "target_amount": 50000000,
    "start_date": "2026-04-01T00:00:00Z",
    "end_date": "2026-06-01T00:00:00Z",
    "is_active": true
}

###

### Get Detail Campaign by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenant/campaigns/{{campaignId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update Campaign
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tenant/campaigns/{{campaignId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Pembebasan Lahan Parkir Masjid (Revisi)",
    "description": "Donasi untuk pembebasan lahan parkir seluas 250m2.",
    "target_amount": 75000000,
    "is_active": true
}

### ============================================================================
### 4. MODUL FINANCE - TRANSACTIONS (ADMIN TENANT)
### ============================================================================

### Get All Transactions in a Campaign
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenant/campaigns/{{campaignId}}/transactions?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================================================
### 5. MODUL FINANCE - PUBLIC ENDPOINTS (JEMAAH / WEBSITE)
### ============================================================================
# Catatan: Endpoint publik tidak memerlukan Authorization Header

### Get All Active Campaigns for Public
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/{{hostname}}/campaigns?page=1&limit=10

###

### Get Campaign Detail by Slug (Ganti slug sesuai yang di-generate)
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/{{hostname}}/campaigns/penambahan-ac-aula

###

### Get Public Donors (Transparansi - Hanya yang PAID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/{{hostname}}/campaigns/{{campaignId}}/donors?page=1&limit=10


### Get Campaign Detail by Slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/public/{{hostname}}/campaigns/penambahan-ac-aula

### Create Donation Checkout (Generate Midtrans URL)
POST {{baseUrl}}/public/{{hostname}}/campaigns/{{campaignId}}/donate
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "donor_name": "Pison Golda",
    "is_anonymous": false,
    "amount": 50000
}